					<msContents class="#CM">
						<summary><p>Various notes by Édouard Ariel, on Indian sciences mostly, but also on other topics.</p>
<p>Various papers and quires of various format bound in one volume: notes, extracts of books copied, lists of vocabulary, dialogues in French translated into Tamil, etc. Subject-headers of top right of rectos.</p>

<p>The volume contains:
  
  <list rend="numbered">
    
    <item><locus facs="0">f1-f2</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">Inde. mathématiques.</quote>.</item>
      
  <item><locus facs="0">f3-f16</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">mesures hindoues</quote>.</item>
  
  <item><locus facs="0">f17-f18</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">mesures monnaies</quote>.</item>
  
    <item><locus facs="0">f19</locus>: TBC.</item>
  
  <item><locus facs="0">f20-f21</locus>: letter (dated 1818) in French to the president of the "Tribunal de la Chaudrie" by residents of Mahé.</item>
              
  <item><locus facs="0">f22-f23</locus>: letter (dated 1843) in French to the chief administrator of Mahé by residents of Mahé.</item>
              
  <item><locus facs="0">f24</locus>: list of Tamil vocabulary.</item>
              
  <item><locus facs="0">f25-f27</locus>: list of plants (under their Indian names) and their properties.</item>
              
  <item><locus facs="0">f28-f29</locus>: list of vocabulary in English, Tulu, Coorg, Toda.</item>
              
  <item><locus facs="0">f30-f34</locus>: list of Toda vocabulary.</item>
              
  <item><locus facs="0">f35</locus>: list of <unclear>Booroo</unclear> vocabulary.</item>
     
  <item><locus facs="0">f36-f41</locus>: list of vocabulary (<quote xml:lang="en">Glossary of terms which occur in this volume <gap reason="ellipsis"/></quote>).</item>
              
  <item><locus facs="0">f42</locus>: letter in French.</item>
     
  <item><locus facs="0">f43</locus>: TBC.</item>
     
  <item><locus facs="0">f44</locus>: Nāgarī characters taken form an inscription from Karnataka.</item>
     
  <item><locus facs="0">f45</locus>: TBC.</item>     
         
  <item><locus facs="0">f46-f48</locus>: biography of Beschi in Tamil.</item>     
         
  <item><locus facs="0">f49-f56</locus>: <quote xml:lang="ta">navamāṉa cētikaḷ</quote>. List of events from 1505 to 1849.</item>     
         
  <item><locus facs="0">f57</locus>: title page <quote xml:lang="fr">Divers Vocabulaires ou Recueils <gap reason="ellipsis"/></quote>.</item>     
         
  <item><locus facs="0">f58-f67</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">Nomenclature des comestibles en usage parmi les indiens &amp; des denrées qu’ils consomment</quote>. List of Tamil vocabulary.</item> 
  
  <item><locus facs="0">f68</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">Instruments aratoires suivant l’arrêté</quote>.</item> 
    
  <item><locus facs="0">f69</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">Grains divers</quote>.</item> 
    
  <item><locus facs="0">f70-72</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">Explication de plusieurs mots bengali en Français par lettres alphabétiques</quote>. Bilingual list in Bengali (transcribed) and French.</item>   
    
  <item><locus facs="0">f73-76</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">Termes grammaticaux</quote>. French and Telugu translations.</item>   
    
  <item><locus facs="0">f77</locus>: <quote xml:lang="fr">Termes de droit</quote>. French and Telugu translations.</item> 
    
  <item><locus facs="0">f78</locus>: document in Tamil (1848).</item> 
    
  <item><locus facs="0">f79-108</locus>: list of vocabulary.</item>     

  <item><locus facs="0">f109-f162</locus>: dialogues in French with (incomplete) Tamil translation (f109-f118), followed by a list of vocabulary in French with (incomplete) Tamil translation (f119-f162).</item>     
       
  </list>
</p>



